interpretation: The "spouting whale" card represents emotional release and communication. Like a whale that rises to the surface to spout water, you may need to let out your feelings and express yourself in order to find clarity and peace. This card can also signify intuition and inner wisdom, reminding you to trust your instincts and listen to your inner voice. However, be mindful not to get too caught up in your emotions and lose sight of practicality and logic. Keywords associated with this card include: emotion, expression, intuition, communication, clarity, wisdom, balance. When this card appears, take a moment to reflect on your emotional state and how you can effectively communicate your needs and desires to those around you. Trust your intuition, but also remain grounded in reality. Overall, the "spouting whale" card urges you to find balance between your emotions and your practical side.
